The scripts located in automation_checklist are tools to help automate creating, updating, and marking the google sheets checklists that QA uses to track regression testing.

To use the tools, copy this scripts over into your script editor.

In an open google sheets:
1. Go to Tools > Script Editor
2. Click on the '+' next to 'Files'
3. Click 'script'
4. copy over script

checklist_common.gs will need to be edited. Parts that need to be edited are marked with a #EDIT THIS above it

The tools left as they are right now will generate the following checklist shown in checklist_example.png
